This is my first attempt at converting my PS1 to PSP games. The more you play this game the better it seems to get. The general rating at the time was 7/10.

Just put this folder into the PSP/Game directory and all should be ok. I have tested it on 3.71 33m-3 custom firmware and I think it will work upto 3.8 33m-5 as well. Not sure on firmware lower or higher than this so you will have to try it for yourself.

The reason why I have started doing this is because some of my purchased games are starting to loose the data and/or have errors on them. I can only put this down to the age of them (some over 10years old now). I will try to put a different one on every 2 weeks so look out for my next one soon.
